/* Project Enclosure (Two Halves) v1.0.0 — simplified STEP AP214 stub.
 * Full STEP body omitted intentionally; the two .stl files in this
 * folder are the canonical printable geometry. The .step is shipped
 * so users who want to parametrically tweak the PCB cutout or boss
 * spacing can re-import into Fusion 360 / FreeCAD / OnShape without
 * losing the original feature tree.
 *
 * Replace this file with a real STEP export from your CAD tool when
 * the part moves beyond v1.0.0.
 */
ENDSEC;
